Company Overview of Deka Investment GmbH



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Deka Investment GmbH  primarily provides its savings banks, insurance companies, and pension funds. It launches and manages equity, fixed income, and balanced mutual funds and hedge funds for its clients. The firm invests in the public equity and fixed income markets. It was founded in 1993 and is based in Frankfurt Main, Germany. Deka Investment GmbH operates as a subsidiary of Dekabank Deutsche Girozentrale.


Mainzer Landstrasse 16Frankfurt Main,  60325GermanyFounded in 1993



Fax: 49 69 7147 1376

www.dekabank.de/db/en/products-solutions/master-investment-company/master-investment-company.jsp







