deka investment gmbh
Private Company









Company Profile
Sector: Financials
Industry: Asset Management
Sub-Industry: Investment Management
Deka Investment GmbH operates as an investment management firm. The Company offers portfolio management, retirement and wealth planning, and advisory services to individuals, institutions, trusts, private funds, charitable organizations, and investment companies. Deka Investment serves customers worldwide.




